        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Investing in Our Communities Act</b></p> <p>This bill reinstates the exclusion from gross income for interest on certain bonds issued to advance the refunding of a prior bond issue. The exclusion was repealed for bonds issued after 2017.</p>]]>
        </text>
